commit.message:
libgomp: Regenerate configure files with automake 1.15.1

libgomp/ChangeLog:
	* Makefile.in: Regenerate with automake 1.15.1.
	* aclocal.m4: Likewise.
	* configure: Likewise.
	* testsuite/Makefile.in: Likewise.
